### MoodMix API — Manual tests
### Requires REST Client extension in VSCode (or JetBrains HTTP client)

@base = http://localhost:8000
@admin_key = 2cd3da40fe2960f184a0d2a764adcb43d5b9eeb0377a334901476c7f8d08de1f

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Health
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{base}}/api/health


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Genres
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all genres
GET {{base}}/api/genres


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Search — 0 sliders (random browse)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Random mixes, no filters
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?limit=5

### Random — jazz only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?genres=jazz&limit=5

### Random — instrumental only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?instrumental=true&limit=5

### Random — page 2 (stable order with seed)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?seed=0.42&limit=5&offset=5


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Search — 1 slider
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Dark only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.7&limit=5

### Bright only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=0.7&limit=5

### Very chill only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?energy=-0.8&limit=5

### Electronic only
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?instrumentation=0.7&limit=5


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Search — 2 sliders
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Dark + chill
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.6&energy=-0.5&limit=5

### Bright + organic
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=0.6&instrumentation=-0.6&limit=5


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Search — 3 sliders (full vector search)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Dark + chill + electronic (synthwave / dark ambient vibes)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.7&energy=-0.5&instrumentation=0.7&limit=20

### Bright + chill + organic (café jazz / bossa nova)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=0.7&energy=-0.5&instrumentation=-0.6&limit=20

### Neutral + dynamic + electronic (deep house)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=0.0&energy=0&instrumentation=0.6&limit=20

### Dark + dynamic + electronic (drum & bass)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.5&energy=0.7&instrumentation=0.6&limit=20


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Search — genre + sliders combined
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Lo-Fi, dark, chill
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.3&energy=-0.5&genres=lo-fi&limit=5

### Jazz, bright, organic
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=0.5&instrumentation=-0.6&genres=jazz&limit=5

### Ambient, very dark
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?mood=-0.7&energy=-0.8&genres=ambient&limit=5

### Multiple genres
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/search?genres=lo-fi,hip-hop&limit=5


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# AI Search (rate limited: 5/min)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Rainy day coffee shop
POST {{base}}/api/mixes/ai-search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query": "rainy day coffee shop vibes"}

### Dark electronic for coding
POST {{base}}/api/mixes/ai-search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query": "dark electronic music for late night coding"}

### Sunny morning
POST {{base}}/api/mixes/ai-search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query": "chill sunny café"}

### Chill piano
POST {{base}}/api/mixes/ai-search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query": "peaceful piano music for reading"}


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Single mix + report unavailable
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get single mix (replace with a real ID from a search result)
GET {{base}}/api/mixes/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Report mix as unavailable
POST {{base}}/api/mixes/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/report-unavailable


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Admin endpoints
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Trigger channel crawl
POST {{base}}/api/admin/crawl/channel
X-API-Key: {{admin_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel_id": "UCRmBxxF1eCDIjyG10P_mRiw",
  "channel_name": "Starburst",
  "max_videos": 10
}
